Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}衛生委員長 能把那個也拿來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}OK 是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在回味赤道祭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不止是這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}修好艦船以後 我們就要參加珀爾修斯作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們只是協助而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 說不定又會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於覺得和晴風號上的各位成為一家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
