Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:14.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}静かに燃える世界　始まりはここから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夜空が終わりを告げるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:24.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ひとすじの光が　胸に秘めた声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:28.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}解き放つ　闇を裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:33.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}枯れるよりいっそ　散り急ぐ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:38.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷い　歩く術を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:46.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}千の波に　呑まれた心じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君さえ守れない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:54.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動　鳴り止まぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:59.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}忘れられぬ傷を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:04.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}今もかすかな残像　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:09.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界が待ってる　明日の産声を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:14.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:22.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう未来と過去が交差する　百年目の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:14.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一切都始於這靜靜燃燒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}在長夜將明之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:24.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一道光芒 一聲發自靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:28.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}衝破束縛 撕裂黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:33.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}尋求著歸宿的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:38.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷茫地邁足前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:46.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}這顆被波濤掩去的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}甚至沒辦法保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:54.06,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪 就像要跳出來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:59.33,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}留下無法忘卻的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:04.33,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}希望這微弱的殘影 永遠不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:09.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界正在等待 屬於明日的嬰啼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:14.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪 千萬不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:22.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}是的 這是一首交錯著過去與未來的百年長歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好 這裡是作戰總部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是福內 你們那裡的情況發生變化了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}富士山頂的超視距雷達發現了武藏號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它不是去菲律賓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主力艦隊來不及回來 但是靠你的艦隊還能攔住它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們盡力 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏號目前位於伊豆半島西南10海浬處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}推測正以18節的航速朝40度方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我艦正以35節的航速追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學校發來的指示 是在藍色人魚部隊抵達之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以保證自己的安全為優先 繼續跟蹤武藏號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還說這次別遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們都提前出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我們才離武藏號最近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美波同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我認為武藏號上的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也和比叡號、施佩伯爵號上的同學一樣 感染了病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以也能像之前那樣去救他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們能做些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮也換上了新的五英吋炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指揮儀也徹底換新了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是說啊 魚雷射擊指揮儀也換成新型的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的肌膚摸起來太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有了你 我終於不用算三角函數了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好想快點來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:43.90,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.12,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水槍也維修過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.21,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們就依照學校的指示 支援藍色人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏號的裝甲和火力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我們是完全不同等級的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也對 讓藍色人魚的艦隊執行計劃比較妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對方可是武藏號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們也得加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.16,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.39,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我方部隊位於石垣島以南 航速40節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定會盡快追上目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主力艦隊大部分都在菲律賓以東
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}集中攻擊的做法適得其反了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能趕到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有以防萬一而留在九州附近的平野部長別動隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有其他能調遣的艦船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一艘艦船還在船塢整修 能否出動還是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大約3小時後 武藏號就會進入浦賀水路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.43,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\p1\fscy150\fscx50\t(100,1000,0,\fscx1200)\1c&H6634D5&\1a20\pos(1166,434)}m 10 0 l 10 -10 l 10 -10 l -10 -10 l -10 10 l 10 10  {\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.43,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord0\1c&H340E21&\pos(966,404)}絕對防禦線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴風號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大約2小時後將趕上武藏號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發現一艘艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷10度 水平線處 航向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷達也探測到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}方位角右舷90度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目測閃光 目標開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迴避 右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢慢拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮開火 炮彈正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 開火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}採取威脅性射擊 或許會更有利迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 請下指示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍人來訊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「晴風號需要立刻撤離當前海域」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撤退？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍人發來了撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本艦隊將強制停止右舷前方武藏號的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突擊組請注意 武藏號的船員都是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盡可能避免肉搏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦隊聽令 90度左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦隊居然能轉得這麼整齊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二號艦 四號艦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使用火箭助飛魚雷攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火箭助飛魚雷 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}厲害 全都打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這下武藏號應該就會停下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:13.95,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦橋暫時交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏號情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏號已停止攻擊 但受損情況不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}速度沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一號艦 三號艦 90度右轉 開始突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一號艦 三號艦 主炮射擊 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功破壞目標右舷副炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二號艦 四號艦 使用火箭助飛魚雷攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火箭助飛魚雷 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發生故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}追…追蹤系統發生錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你到底是怎麼了 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍色人魚已經到了 但我們也有我們的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輪機就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗緒 你跟輪機長去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輪機運轉就靠我們四個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早就聽說電子儀器會發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魚雷發射管 準備發射魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使用非追蹤魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非追蹤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各炮台剩餘彈藥 合計約為90至100
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的航向沒變 仍在朝浦賀水路方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的船…正在攻擊藍色人魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先弄清情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後再找機會停船 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天就能和其他班級會合了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海艦橋傳來消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷60度方向發現貨船 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 沒人回話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}射擊指揮儀 請求回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}角田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冷靜點 出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們…她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不算難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 糧食與飲水有保障了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火控室 輪機室 舵手室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全都被她們占領了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們聽不進我說話 就像被什麼操縱了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用這個能發射出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過電源是使用電池 大概只能撐幾分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是武藏號 這裡是武藏號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當前位置阿森松島西北10海浬處 發生緊急狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當前位置阿森松島西北 阿森松島西北
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請求救援 請求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 快來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我們學校的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴風號…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使用非追蹤魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一戰速 右舵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}0度直航
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦隊聽令 發射魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}四號艦 中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍人中彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}中彈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍人四號艦 速度減慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魚雷命中 一 二 三 四
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}四號艦 艦尾遭到炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}四號艦報告 「我艦無法前進 無法繼續戰鬥」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}普通魚雷已經用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦隊繞進目標右後方 準備強行登艦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有艦船 立刻準備放出無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一 二 三號艦 無人機已起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏號有什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 炮口轉向了無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎在警戒無人機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右轉180度 反轉航向的同時讓無人機繼續靠近目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 是無人機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們打算用無人機遮蔽視線？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦隊聽令 開始射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}四號副炮 嚴重受損
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}速射炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全速退避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知床同學 距離拉遠一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍人的船隻剩一艘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長和副艦長倒是快點回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想攔下武藏號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也想幫幫藍色人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還想救出武藏號上的同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一想到要是讓晴風號的各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遇上了什麼危險就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平賀艦隊 只剩最後一艘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我校船隻發送命令 請她們立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外 去接通國土安全委員會的熱線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}避難工作準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已在東京灣全境拉響了警報
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不知道趕不趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}橫須賀女子海洋學校接通了熱線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是校長宗谷真雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我宣布 依據「海洋安全保障法」第12條
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}橫須賀女子海洋學校進入緊急狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我即將登艦指揮 不再接受聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能交給她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交給她這個來島的巴御前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼這麼叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}十五年前 在我國領海裡有一個四處作惡的武裝海盜團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個校長只憑一艘船就全滅了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍人發來聯絡 各位注意收聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們來吸引武藏號的注意 晴風號抓準機會立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重複一遍 晴風號需要立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聯絡結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備投放水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們…什麼都做不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣看著武藏號開進浦賀水路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮隨時可以發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦橋 能保持現在的航速嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 飯糰做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有咖哩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}年糕小豆湯也做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦首B2區進水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關上水密門 動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 我艦應當如何行動 請您決…決…決…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼尻不尻的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的 我想說的是決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}決斷 你要我怎麼決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我們至今能得救都是運氣好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本不是我的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們都是我重要的家人 一想到可能會失去你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把艦長架到艦橋去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你跟我過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣艦橋就聽不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種時候你想說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}簡單來說 在鰹魚生魚片上塗美乃滋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實是很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換句話說 雖然我和輪機長的性格完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但正是因為這份不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}合在一起時才更有一種獨特的風味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外祭典上打太鼓的時候也不會總是打鼓面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不把鼓邊敲得梆梆作響 聲音永遠都會鬆鬆垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就像我和小黑一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fn華康布丁體\bord0\1vc(&H9140D8&,&H4D19BA&,&H9140D8&,&H4D19BA&)\3c&H844CBD&\frz354.1\move(496,488,492,496,0,2619)}咱們是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吧 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的意思應該是 互補不足才算真正的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宗谷同學 能輔佐艦長的只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣 聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完美解決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輪機長 你只是想擺這個pose而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發現目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三發主炮炮彈 目標是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想成為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的美乃滋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 說得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還真這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美乃滋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長 你想表達什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想成為艦長的後盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.04,0:20:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長只要像原來那樣作出決斷 展開行動 拿出運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其他的事都交給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 都交給晴風號上的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼想的不止有我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 我們還能做到很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也早就不逃來逃去的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要我做什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}皇天不負苦心人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:21:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果副艦長是美乃滋的話 我就是芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大海的夥伴齊心合力 哪有衝不破的暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白…各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武藏號傳來燈光信號 正在解讀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貴艦應當繼續與我艦拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}靠近我艦將非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮剩餘彈藥充足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香香她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那更得救她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五十六 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}左舷 準備開火 發射魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目標是300度方向的武藏號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目標航向30度 目標速度18節
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第五戰速 向340度方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 晴風號傳來了燈光信號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點解讀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我艦將救援貴艦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重複 我艦將救援貴艦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:25.05,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,495)}漂搖在大艦巨炮面前
